snippet.title: Aquaman 2, The Lord of the Rings Amazon Series, Hobbs & Shaw 2, Expendables 4... KinoCheck News
snippet.description:
This time in the #KinoCheckNews "Black Widow" vs Disney, "Hawkeye", "The Expendables 4", "Spider-Man: No Way Home" Trailer, "Aquaman 2: The lost Kingdom", "Fast and Furious: Hobbs and Shaw 2", "The Expendables 4" etc.| Subscribe ➤ https://abo.yt/ki | 2021 Movie News Show | More News https://KinoCheck.com/news 

00:00 Hawkeye
The MCU keeps growing, not only on the big screen, but especially on Disney+. One of the next big hits in Marvel's series line-up will be "Hawkeye". As has been known for several days, the series will be available on Disney+ from November 24th and will include eight episodes, which will then be released weekly...https://kinocheck.com/news/f231tq

01:04 Hobbs and Shaw 2
Recently, actor Dwayne Johnson officially announced his exit from the upcoming two "Fast and Furious" movies 10 and 11. After several arguments with Vin Diesel and poor prospects for reconciliation, the 49-year-old decided to turn his back on the main series. Till the end, some still believed that it must be somehow possible to bring back Luke Hobbs...https://kinocheck.com/news/3mz9by

02:39 The Expendables 4
Hollywood legend Sylvester Stallone has been in the movie business for an incredible 52 years! In the last ten years, there has been at least one film with his contribution in theaters in almost every year. Not bad for a now 75-year-old, but it seems like the "Rocky" star still hasn't had enough...https://kinocheck.com/news/a8z1dm

03:29 The Lord of the Rings Amazon series
Amazon's most expensive series of all time has been in production for some time now, namely "The Lord of the Rings". After Peter Jackson's film trilogy and the "Hobbit" spin-off, fans are already eagerly awaiting the giant project. Since we must still wait quite a while until the official release on September 2, 2022, we are all the more pleased that a first image from the series has now been published...https://kinocheck.com/news/f5k8n6

04:56 Aquaman and the lost Kingdom
It should not have escaped anyone's notice that the legal matter between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp is still being fought with no holds barred. After Johnny Depp has so far struggled against devastating financial losses and defamation on a grand scale, a new campaign against his ex-wife is now getting underway. In recent days and weeks, calls for Heard to be fired from the "Aquaman" sequel have been accumulating...https://kinocheck.com/news/h2bjtv

06:11 Scarlett Johansson vs Disney
The first Marvel movie from the fourth phase, "Black Widow", has barely been released, and already there is a lot of turmoil behind the scenes. The reason for this is the release policy of the streaming service Disney+, which is causing the actors massive financial losses. This is also the case for Scarlett Johansson, who has filed a lawsuit against her former employer, according to the Wall Street Journal. The accusation: breach of contract on the part of the movie giant...https://kinocheck.com/news/imzuta

07:44 Spider-Man 3: No Way Home
In recent weeks, we have often reported on merchandise leaks and numerous other rumors regarding "Spider-Man: No Way Home". But one important marketing component is still missing from the most anticipated movie of 2021 - an actual trailer. Indeed, a trailer that confirms, or at least doesn't debunk, all the rumors that have been circulating...
